pokemons.name: bulbasaur
pokemons.quote:
A strange seed was
planted on its
back at birth. The plant sprouts
and grows with
this POKéMON.

pokemons.name: ivysaur
pokemons.quote:
When the bulb on
its back grows
large, it appears to lose the
ability to stand
on its hind legs.

pokemons.name: venusaur
pokemons.quote:
The plant blooms
when it is
absorbing solar energy. It stays
on the move to
seek sunlight.

pokemons.name: charmander
pokemons.quote:
Obviously prefers
hot places. When
it rains, steam is said to spout
from the tip of
its tail.

pokemons.name: charmeleon
pokemons.quote:
When it swings
its burning tail,
it elevates the temperature to
unbearably high
levels.

pokemons.name: charizard
pokemons.quote:
Spits fire that
is hot enough to
melt boulders. Known to cause
forest fires
unintentionally.

pokemons.name: squirtle
pokemons.quote:
Shoots water at
prey while in the
water. Withdraws into
its shell when in
danger.

pokemons.name: wartortle
pokemons.quote:
When tapped, this
POKéMON will pull
in its head, but its tail will
still stick out a
little bit.

pokemons.name: blastoise
pokemons.quote:
It deliberately
makes itself heavy
so it can with­ stand the recoil
of the water jets
it fires.

pokemons.name: caterpie
pokemons.quote:
It releases a stench from its red
antenna to repel enemies. It
grows by molting repeatedly.

pokemons.name: metapod
pokemons.quote:
This POKéMON is
vulnerable to
attack while its shell is soft,
exposing its weak
and tender body.

pokemons.name: butterfree
pokemons.quote:
In battle, it
flaps its wings
at high speed to release highly
toxic dust into
the air.

pokemons.name: weedle
pokemons.quote:
Often found in
forests, eating
leaves. It has a sharp
venomous stinger
on its head.

pokemons.name: kakuna
pokemons.quote:
Almost incapable
of moving, this
POKéMON can only harden its shell
to protect itself
from predators.

pokemons.name: beedrill
pokemons.quote:
Flies at high
speed and attacks
using its large venomous stingers
on its forelegs
and tail.

pokemons.name: pidgey
pokemons.quote:
A common sight in
forests and woods.
It flaps its wings at ground
level to kick up
blinding sand.

pokemons.name: pidgeotto
pokemons.quote:
Very protective
of its sprawling
territorial area, this POKéMON will
fiercely peck at
any intruder.

pokemons.name: pidgeot
pokemons.quote:
When hunting, it
skims the surface
of water at high speed to pick off
unwary prey such
as MAGIKARP.

pokemons.name: rattata
pokemons.quote:
Bites anything
when it attacks.
Small and very quick, it is a
common sight in
many places.

pokemons.name: raticate
pokemons.quote:
It uses its whis­
kers to maintain
its balance. It apparently
slows down if
they are cut off.

pokemons.name: spearow
pokemons.quote:
Il est incapable de voler à haute altitude.
Il se déplace très vite pour protéger
son territoire.

pokemons.name: fearow
pokemons.quote:
With its huge and
magnificent wings,
it can keep aloft without ever
having to land
for rest.

pokemons.name: ekans
pokemons.quote:
Moves silently
and stealthily.
Eats the eggs of birds, such as
PIDGEY and
SPEAROW, whole.

pokemons.name: arbok
pokemons.quote:
It is rumored that
the ferocious
warning markings on its belly
differ from area
to area.

pokemons.name: pikachu
pokemons.quote:
最近發表了聚集大量皮卡丘
來建造發電廠的計畫。

pokemons.name: raichu
pokemons.quote:
Its tail discharges electricity into
the ground, protecting it from
getting shocked.

pokemons.name: sandshrew
pokemons.quote:
Burrows deep
underground in
arid locations far from water.
It only emerges
to hunt for food.

pokemons.name: sandslash
pokemons.quote:
Curls up into a
spiny ball when
threatened. It can roll while
curled up to
attack or escape.

pokemons.name: nidoran-f
pokemons.quote:
Although small,
its venomous
barbs render this POKéMON dangerous.
The female has
smaller horns.

pokemons.name: nidorina
pokemons.quote:
The female's horn
develops slowly.
Prefers physical attacks such as
clawing and
biting.

pokemons.name: nidoqueen
pokemons.quote:
Its hard scales
provide strong
protection. It uses its hefty
bulk to execute
powerful moves.

pokemons.name: nidoran-m
pokemons.quote:
Saca las orejas por encima de la hierba para explorar
el territorio. Le protege su cuerno venenoso.

pokemons.name: nidorino
pokemons.quote:
An aggressive
POKéMON that is
quick to attack. The horn on its
head secretes a
powerful venom.

pokemons.name: nidoking
pokemons.quote:
One swing of its mighty tail can
snap a telephone pole as if it were
a matchstick.

pokemons.name: clefairy
pokemons.quote:
Its magical and
cute appeal has
many admirers. It is rare and
found only in
certain areas.

pokemons.name: clefable
pokemons.quote:
A timid fairy
POKéMON that is
rarely seen. It will run and hide
the moment it
senses people.

pokemons.name: vulpix
pokemons.quote:
At the time of
birth, it has
just one tail. The tail splits
from its tip as
it grows older.

pokemons.name: ninetales
pokemons.quote:
Very smart and
very vengeful.
Grabbing one of its many tails
could result in a
1000-year curse.

pokemons.name: jigglypuff
pokemons.quote:
When its huge eyes
light up, it sings
a mysteriously soothing melody
that lulls its
enemies to sleep.

pokemons.name: wigglytuff
pokemons.quote:
The body is soft
and rubbery. When
angered, it will suck in air and
inflate itself to
an enormous size.

pokemons.name: zubat
pokemons.quote:
Forms colonies in
perpetually dark
places. Uses ultrasonic waves
to identify and
approach targets.

pokemons.name: golbat
pokemons.quote:
Once it strikes,
it will not stop
draining energy from the victim
even if it gets
too heavy to fly.

pokemons.name: oddish
pokemons.quote:
During the day,
it keeps its face
buried in the ground. At night,
it wanders around
sowing its seeds.

pokemons.name: gloom
pokemons.quote:
It secretes a
sticky, drool-like
honey. Although sweet, it smells
too repulsive to
get very close.

pokemons.name: vileplume
pokemons.quote:
It has the world's
largest petals.
With every step, the petals shake
out heavy clouds
of toxic pollen.

pokemons.name: paras
pokemons.quote:
Burrows to suck
tree roots. The
mushrooms on its back grow by draw­
ing nutrients from
the bug host.

pokemons.name: parasect
pokemons.quote:
A host-parasite
pair in which the
parasite mushroom has taken over the
host bug. Prefers
damp places.

pokemons.name: venonat
pokemons.quote:
Lives in the
shadows of tall
trees where it eats insects. It
is attracted by
light at night.

pokemons.name: venomoth
pokemons.quote:
The dust-like
scales covering
its wings are color coded to
indicate the kinds
of poison it has.

pokemons.name: diglett
pokemons.quote:
Lives about one
yard underground
where it feeds on plant roots. It
sometimes appears
above ground.

pokemons.name: dugtrio
pokemons.quote:
A team of DIGLETT
triplets.
It triggers huge earthquakes by
burrowing 60 miles
underground.

pokemons.name: meowth
pokemons.quote:
Es de naturaleza nocturna. Le atraen los objetos
brillantes.

pokemons.name: persian
pokemons.quote:
Although its fur
has many admirers,
it is tough to raise as a pet
because of its
fickle meanness.

pokemons.name: psyduck
pokemons.quote:
While lulling its
enemies with its
vacant look, this wily POKéMON will
use psychokinetic
powers.

pokemons.name: golduck
pokemons.quote:
Often seen swim­
ming elegantly by
lake shores. It is often mistaken
for the Japanese
monster, Kappa.

pokemons.name: mankey
pokemons.quote:
Extremely quick to
anger. It could
be docile one moment then
thrashing away
the next instant.

pokemons.name: primeape
pokemons.quote:
Always furious
and tenacious to
boot. It will not abandon chasing
its quarry until
it is caught.

pokemons.name: growlithe
pokemons.quote:
Very protective
of its territory.
It will bark and bite to repel
intruders from
its space.

pokemons.name: arcanine
pokemons.quote:
A POKéMON that
has been admired
since the past for its beauty.
It runs agilely
as if on wings.

pokemons.name: poliwag
pokemons.quote:
Its newly grown
legs prevent it
from running. It appears to prefer
swimming than
trying to stand.

pokemons.name: poliwhirl
pokemons.quote:
Capable of living
in or out of
water. When out of water, it
sweats to keep
its body slimy.

pokemons.name: poliwrath
pokemons.quote:
An adept swimmer
at both the front
crawl and breast stroke. Easily
overtakes the best
human swimmers.

pokemons.name: abra
pokemons.quote:
Dieses Pokémon schläft 18 Stunden am Tag.
Bei Gefahr teleportiert es sich in Sicherheit,
ohne dabei aufzuwachen.

pokemons.name: kadabra
pokemons.quote:
It emits special
alpha waves from
its body that induce headaches
just by being
close by.

pokemons.name: alakazam
pokemons.quote:
Its brain can out­
perform a super­
computer. Its intelligence
quotient is said
to be 5,000.

pokemons.name: machop
pokemons.quote:
Loves to build
its muscles.
It trains in all styles of martial
arts to become
even stronger.

pokemons.name: machoke
pokemons.quote:
Its muscular body
is so powerful, it
must wear a power save belt to be
able to regulate
its motions.

pokemons.name: machamp
pokemons.quote:
Using its heavy
muscles, it throws
powerful punches that can send the
victim clear over
the horizon.

pokemons.name: bellsprout
pokemons.quote:
Even though its body is extremely
skinny, it is blindingly fast
when catching its prey.

pokemons.name: weepinbell
pokemons.quote:
Escupe Polvo Veneno para envenenar al enemigo y,
luego, lo liquida con Ácido.

pokemons.name: victreebel
pokemons.quote:
Said to live in
huge colonies
deep in jungles, although no one
has ever returned
from there.

pokemons.name: tentacool
pokemons.quote:
Son corps est principalement composé d’eau.
Ses yeux cristallins projettent d’étranges rayons.

pokemons.name: tentacruel
pokemons.quote:
80개의 촉수를 자유롭게
움직인다. 찔리면 독이 퍼져
극심한 고통을 겪게 된다.

pokemons.name: geodude
pokemons.quote:
Found in fields
and mountains.
Mistaking them for boulders,
people often step
or trip on them.

pokemons.name: graveler
pokemons.quote:
Rolls down slopes
to move. It rolls
over any obstacle without slowing
or changing its
direction.

pokemons.name: golem
pokemons.quote:
Its boulder-like
body is extremely
hard. It can easily withstand
dynamite blasts
without damage.

pokemons.name: ponyta
pokemons.quote:
Its hooves are 10
times harder than
diamonds. It can trample anything
completely flat
in little time.

pokemons.name: rapidash
pokemons.quote:
Very competitive,
this POKéMON will
chase anything that moves fast
in the hopes of
racing it.

pokemons.name: slowpoke
pokemons.quote:
Incredibly slow
and dopey. It
takes 5 seconds for it to feel
pain when under
attack.

pokemons.name: slowbro
pokemons.quote:
The SHELLDER that
is latched onto
SLOWPOKE's tail is said to feed
on the host's left
over scraps.

pokemons.name: magnemite
pokemons.quote:
Uses anti-gravity
to stay suspended.
Appears without warning and uses
THUNDER WAVE and
similar moves.

pokemons.name: magneton
pokemons.quote:
Formed by several
MAGNEMITEs linked
together. They frequently appear
when sunspots
flare up.

pokemons.name: farfetchd
pokemons.quote:
The sprig of
green onions it
holds is its weapon. It is
used much like a
metal sword.

pokemons.name: doduo
pokemons.quote:
A bird that makes
up for its poor
flying with its fast foot speed.
Leaves giant
footprints.

pokemons.name: dodrio
pokemons.quote:
Uses its three
brains to execute
complex plans. While two heads
sleep, one head
stays awake.

pokemons.name: seel
pokemons.quote:
The protruding
horn on its head
is very hard. It is used for
bashing through
thick ice.

pokemons.name: dewgong
pokemons.quote:
Stores thermal
energy in its
body. Swims at a steady 8 knots
even in intensely
cold waters.

pokemons.name: grimer
pokemons.quote:
Appears in filthy
areas. Thrives by
sucking up polluted sludge
that is pumped
out of factories.

pokemons.name: muk
pokemons.quote:
Thickly covered
with a filthy,
vile sludge. It is so toxic, even
its footprints
contain poison.

pokemons.name: shellder
pokemons.quote:
Its hard shell
repels any kind
of attack. It is vulnerable
only when its
shell is open.

pokemons.name: cloyster
pokemons.quote:
CLOYSTER that live
in seas with harsh
tidal currents grow large, sharp
spikes on their
shells.

pokemons.name: gastly
pokemons.quote:
Almost invisible,
this gaseous
POKéMON cloaks the target and
puts it to sleep
without notice.

pokemons.name: haunter
pokemons.quote:
Because of its
ability to slip
through block walls, it is said
to be from an­
other dimension.

pokemons.name: gengar
pokemons.quote:
Under a full moon,
this POKéMON
likes to mimic the shadows of
people and laugh
at their fright.

pokemons.name: onix
pokemons.quote:
As it grows, the
stone portions of
its body harden to become similar
to a diamond, but
colored black.

pokemons.name: drowzee
pokemons.quote:
Puts enemies to
sleep then eats
their dreams. Occasionally gets
sick from eating
bad dreams.

pokemons.name: hypno
pokemons.quote:
When it locks eyes
with an enemy, it
will use a mix of PSI moves such as
HYPNOSIS and
CONFUSION.

pokemons.name: krabby
pokemons.quote:
Its pincers are
not only powerful
weapons, they are used for balance
when walking
sideways.

pokemons.name: kingler
pokemons.quote:
The large pincer
has 10000 hp of
crushing power. However, its huge
size makes it
unwieldy to use.

pokemons.name: voltorb
pokemons.quote:
Usually found in
power plants.
Easily mistaken for a POKé BALL,
they have zapped
many people.

pokemons.name: electrode
pokemons.quote:
It stores electric
energy under very
high pressure. It often explodes
with little or no
provocation.

pokemons.name: exeggcute
pokemons.quote:
Often mistaken
for eggs.
When disturbed, they quickly
gather and attack
in swarms.

pokemons.name: exeggutor
pokemons.quote:
Legend has it that
on rare occasions,
one of its heads will drop off and
continue on as an
EXEGGCUTE.

pokemons.name: cubone
pokemons.quote:
死に別れた　母親の　骨を
頭に　覆っている。寂しいとき
大声で　泣くという。

pokemons.name: marowak
pokemons.quote:
骨に　灯った　呪いの　炎は
いつまでも　治らない　痛みを
体と　心に　残すという。

pokemons.name: hitmonlee
pokemons.quote:
When in a hurry,
its legs lengthen
progressively. It runs smoothly
with extra long,
loping strides.

pokemons.name: hitmonchan
pokemons.quote:
While apparently
doing nothing, it
fires punches in lightning fast
volleys that are
impossible to see.

pokemons.name: lickitung
pokemons.quote:
Its tongue can be
extended like a
chameleon's. It leaves a tingling
sensation when it
licks enemies.

pokemons.name: koffing
pokemons.quote:
Because it stores
several kinds of
toxic gases in its body, it is
prone to exploding
without warning.

pokemons.name: weezing
pokemons.quote:
Where two kinds
of poison gases
meet, 2 KOFFINGs can fuse into a
WEEZING over many
years.

pokemons.name: rhyhorn
pokemons.quote:
Its massive bones
are 1000 times
harder than human bones. It can
easily knock a
trailer flying.

pokemons.name: rhydon
pokemons.quote:
Protected by an
armor-like hide,
it is capable of living in molten
lava of 3,600
degrees.

pokemons.name: chansey
pokemons.quote:
A rare and elusive
POKéMON that is
said to bring happiness to those
who manage to get
it.

pokemons.name: tangela
pokemons.quote:
The whole body is
swathed with wide
vines that are similar to sea­
weed. Its vines
shake as it walks.

pokemons.name: kangaskhan
pokemons.quote:
The infant rarely
ventures out of
its mother's protective pouch
until it is 3
years old.

pokemons.name: horsea
pokemons.quote:
Hace su nido entre los corales. Si se siente en peligro,
escupe tinta y huye.

pokemons.name: seadra
pokemons.quote:
Capable of swim­
ming backwards by
rapidly flapping its wing-like
pectoral fins and
stout tail.

pokemons.name: goldeen
pokemons.quote:
せびれ　むなびれ　おびれが
ゆうがに　たなびくので
みずのおどりこ　とよばれる。

pokemons.name: seaking
pokemons.quote:
In the autumn
spawning season,
they can be seen swimming power­
fully up rivers
and creeks.

pokemons.name: staryu
pokemons.quote:
An enigmatic
POKéMON that can
effortlessly regenerate any
appendage it
loses in battle.

pokemons.name: starmie
pokemons.quote:
Its central core
glows with the
seven colors of the rainbow. Some
people value the
core as a gem.

pokemons.name: mr-mime
pokemons.quote:
If interrupted
while it is
miming, it will slap around the
offender with its
broad hands.

pokemons.name: scyther
pokemons.quote:
With ninja-like
agility and speed,
it can create the illusion that
there is more
than one.

pokemons.name: jynx
pokemons.quote:
Its cries sound like human speech.
However, it is impossible to tell
what it is trying to say.

pokemons.name: electabuzz
pokemons.quote:
Normally found
near power plants,
they can wander away and cause
major blackouts
in cities.

pokemons.name: magmar
pokemons.quote:
Its body always
burns with an
orange glow that enables it to
hide perfectly
among flames.

pokemons.name: pinsir
pokemons.quote:
If it fails to
crush the victim
in its pincers, it will swing it
around and toss
it hard.

pokemons.name: tauros
pokemons.quote:
When it targets
an enemy, it
charges furiously while whipping its
body with its
long tails.

pokemons.name: magikarp
pokemons.quote:
In the distant
past, it was
somewhat stronger than the horribly
weak descendants
that exist today.

pokemons.name: gyarados
pokemons.quote:
Rarely seen in
the wild. Huge
and vicious, it is capable of
destroying entire
cities in a rage.

pokemons.name: lapras
pokemons.quote:
A POKéMON that
has been over­
hunted almost to extinction. It
can ferry people
across the water.

pokemons.name: ditto
pokemons.quote:
It can freely recombine its own cellular structure to
transform into other life-forms.

pokemons.name: eevee
pokemons.quote:
Its genetic code
is irregular.
It may mutate if it is exposed to
radiation from
element STONEs.

pokemons.name: vaporeon
pokemons.quote:
수중에서의 생활에 적합한
몸으로 진화했다.
물에 녹으면 보이지 않게 된다.

pokemons.name: jolteon
pokemons.quote:
It accumulates
negative ions in
the atmosphere to blast out 10000-
volt lightning
bolts.

pokemons.name: flareon
pokemons.quote:
When storing
thermal energy in
its body, its temperature could
soar to over 1600
degrees.

pokemons.name: porygon
pokemons.quote:
A POKéMON that
consists entirely
of programming code. Capable of
moving freely in
cyberspace.

pokemons.name: omanyte
pokemons.quote:
Although long
extinct, in rare
cases, it can be genetically
resurrected from
fossils.

pokemons.name: omastar
pokemons.quote:
Apparently, it
cracked SHELLDER's
shell with its sharp fangs and
sucked out the
insides.

pokemons.name: kabuto
pokemons.quote:
A POKéMON that
was resurrected
from a fossil found in what was
once the ocean
floor eons ago.

pokemons.name: kabutops
pokemons.quote:
Its sleek shape is
perfect for swim­
ming. It slashes prey with its
claws and drains
the body fluids.

pokemons.name: aerodactyl
pokemons.quote:
A ferocious, pre­
historic POKéMON
that goes for the enemy's throat
with its serrated
saw-like fangs.

pokemons.name: snorlax
pokemons.quote:
Very lazy. Just
eats and sleeps.
As its rotund bulk builds, it
becomes steadily
more slothful.

pokemons.name: articuno
pokemons.quote:
A legendary bird
POKéMON that is
said to appear to doomed people who
are lost in icy
mountains.

pokemons.name: zapdos
pokemons.quote:
A legendary bird
POKéMON that is
said to appear from clouds while
dropping enormous
lightning bolts.

pokemons.name: moltres
pokemons.quote:
It is said to be the legendary bird Pokémon of fire.
Every flap of its wings creates a dazzling flare
of flames.

pokemons.name: dratini
pokemons.quote:
Long considered a
mythical POKéMON
until recently when a small
colony was found
living underwater.

pokemons.name: dragonair
pokemons.quote:
A mystical POKéMON
that exudes a
gentle aura. Has the ability
to change climate
conditions.

pokemons.name: dragonite
pokemons.quote:
An extremely
rarely seen
marine POKéMON. Its intelligence
is said to match
that of humans.

pokemons.name: mewtwo
pokemons.quote:
It was created by
a scientist after
years of horrific gene splicing and
DNA engineering
experiments.

pokemons.name: mew
pokemons.quote:
So rare that it
is still said to
be a mirage by many experts. Only
a few people have
seen it worldwide.

pokemons.name: chikorita
pokemons.quote:
A sweet aroma
gently wafts from
the leaf on its head. It is docile
and loves to soak
up the sun's rays.

pokemons.name: bayleef
pokemons.quote:
Die Knospen an seinem Hals geben ein
würziges Aroma ab, das andere aufheitert.

pokemons.name: meganium
pokemons.quote:
The aroma that
rises from its
petals contains a substance that
calms aggressive
feelings.

pokemons.name: cyndaquil
pokemons.quote:
It is timid, and
always curls it­
self up in a ball. If attacked, it
flares up its back
for protection.

pokemons.name: quilava
pokemons.quote:
Be careful if it
turns its back
during battle. It means that it will
attack with the
fire on its back.

pokemons.name: typhlosion
pokemons.quote:
If its rage peaks,
it becomes so hot
that anything that touches it will
instantly go
up in flames.

pokemons.name: totodile
pokemons.quote:
Its well-developed
jaws are powerful
and capable of crushing anything.
Even its trainer
must be careful.

pokemons.name: croconaw
pokemons.quote:
If it loses a
fang, a new one
grows back in its place. There are
always 48 fangs
lining its mouth.

pokemons.name: feraligatr
pokemons.quote:
When it bites with
its massive and
powerful jaws, it shakes its head
and savagely tears
its victim up.

pokemons.name: sentret
pokemons.quote:
A very cautious
POKéMON, it raises
itself up using its tail to get a
better view of its
surroundings.

pokemons.name: furret
pokemons.quote:
The mother puts its offspring to
sleep by curling up around them.
It corners foes with speed.

pokemons.name: hoothoot
pokemons.quote:
It always stands on one foot.
It changes feet so fast,
the movement can rarely be seen.

pokemons.name: noctowl
pokemons.quote:
Its eyes are
specially adapted.
They concentrate even faint light
and enable it to
see in the dark.

pokemons.name: ledyba
pokemons.quote:
It is very timid.
It will be afraid
to move if it is alone. But it will
be active if it is
in a group.

pokemons.name: ledian
pokemons.quote:
When the stars
flicker in the
night sky, it flutters about,
scattering a
glowing powder.

pokemons.name: spinarak
pokemons.quote:
It lies still in
the same pose for
days in its web, waiting for its
unsuspecting prey
to wander close.

pokemons.name: ariados
pokemons.quote:
It spins string
not only from its
rear but also from its mouth. It is
hard to tell which
end is which.

pokemons.name: crobat
pokemons.quote:
It flies so si­
lently through the
dark on its four wings that it may
not be noticed
even when nearby.

pokemons.name: chinchou
pokemons.quote:
It shoots positive
and negative elec­
tricity between the tips of its
two antennae and
zaps its enemies.

pokemons.name: lanturn
pokemons.quote:
The light it emits
is so bright that
it can illuminate the sea's surface
from a depth of
over three miles.

pokemons.name: pichu
pokemons.quote:
It is not yet
skilled at storing
electricity. It may send out a
jolt if amused
or startled.

pokemons.name: cleffa
pokemons.quote:
Si dice che sia facile incontrarlo dove sono
precipitate delle stelle cadenti.

pokemons.name: igglybuff
pokemons.quote:
It has a very soft
body. If it starts
to roll, it will bounce all over
and be impossible
to stop.

pokemons.name: togepi
pokemons.quote:
The shell seems to
be filled with
joy. It is said that it will share
good luck when
treated kindly.

pokemons.name: togetic
pokemons.quote:
They say that it
will appear before
kindhearted, car­ ing people and
shower them with
happiness.

pokemons.name: natu
pokemons.quote:
Because its wings
aren't yet fully
grown, it has to hop to get around.
It is always star­
ing at something.

pokemons.name: xatu
pokemons.quote:
They say that it
stays still and
quiet because it is seeing both the
past and future at
the same time.

pokemons.name: mareep
pokemons.quote:
If static elec­
tricity builds in
its body, its fleece doubles in
volume. Touching
it will shock you.

pokemons.name: flaaffy
pokemons.quote:
As a result of
storing too much
electricity, it developed patches
where even downy
wool won't grow.

pokemons.name: ampharos
pokemons.quote:
The tail's tip
shines brightly
and can be seen from far away. It
acts as a beacon
for lost people.

pokemons.name: bellossom
pokemons.quote:
BELLOSSOM gather
at times and
appear to dance. They say that the
dance is a ritual
to summon the sun.

pokemons.name: marill
pokemons.quote:
The tip of its
tail, which con­
tains oil that is lighter than wa­
ter, lets it swim
without drowning.

pokemons.name: azumarill
pokemons.quote:
会制作填满空气的泡泡。
当露力丽在河里玩的时候，
它就会用这个泡泡包住露力丽。

pokemons.name: sudowoodo
pokemons.quote:
Although it always
pretends to be a
tree, its composi­ tion appears to be
closer to a rock
than a plant.

pokemons.name: politoed
pokemons.quote:
울음소리가 울려 퍼지면
여기저기에서 발챙이와
슈륙챙이들이 모인다.

pokemons.name: hoppip
pokemons.quote:
To keep from being
blown away by the
wind, they gather in clusters. They
do enjoy gentle
breezes, though.

pokemons.name: skiploom
pokemons.quote:
The bloom on top
of its head opens
and closes as the temperature fluc­
tuates up and
down.

pokemons.name: jumpluff
pokemons.quote:
Once it catches
the wind, it deft­
ly controls its cotton-puff spores
to float, even
around the world.

pokemons.name: aipom
pokemons.quote:
Its tail is so
powerful that it
can use it to grab a tree branch and
hold itself up in
the air.

pokemons.name: sunkern
pokemons.quote:
It may drop out of
the sky suddenly.
If attacked by a SPEAROW, it will
violently shake
its leaves.

pokemons.name: sunflora
pokemons.quote:
태양 에너지에서 영양을 만들어낸다.
기온이 높은 낮에는 활발하게 움직이고
태양이 지면 뚝 하니 움직이지 않게 된다.

pokemons.name: yanma
pokemons.quote:
If it flaps its
wings really fast,
it can generate shock waves that
will shatter win­
dows in the area.

pokemons.name: wooper
pokemons.quote:
This POKéMON lives
in cold water. It
will leave the water to search
for food when it
gets cold outside.

pokemons.name: quagsire
pokemons.quote:
This carefree
POKéMON has an
easy-going nature. While swimming, it
always bumps into
boat hulls.

pokemons.name: espeon
pokemons.quote:
It uses the fine
hair that covers
its body to sense air currents and
predict its ene­
my's actions.

pokemons.name: umbreon
pokemons.quote:
When agitated,
this POKéMON pro­
tects itself by spraying poisonous
sweat from its
pores.

pokemons.name: murkrow
pokemons.quote:
Feared and loathed
by many, it is
believed to bring misfortune to all
those who see it
at night.

pokemons.name: slowking
pokemons.quote:
It has incredible
intellect and in­
tuition. Whatever the situation, it
remains calm and
collected.

pokemons.name: misdreavus
pokemons.quote:
It likes playing
mischievous tricks
such as screaming and wailing to
startle people at
night.
